content.en:
# Everything is a Component

Components are functions returning JSX.

### Props
Props are arguments passed to components. They are **read-only**.

```jsx
function Card({ title }) {
  return <h2>{title}</h2>;
}
```

exercise.code:
function Botao({ label, cor }) {
  return <button style={{ backgroundColor: cor }}>{label}</button>;
}

const [nome, setNome] = useState('');
<input value={nome} onChange={e => setNome(e.target.value)} />
<p>Digitando: {nome}</p>

